Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Art and Skill in Work
By: Muhammad
Glossary:
  - Term: Ihsân
    Definition: Sanctifying virtue, spiritual beauty.
---
Allâh has prescribed Ihsân for everything; hence, if you kill, do it
well; and if you slaughter, do it well; and let each one of you
sharpen his knife and let his victim die at once.
